column2: SELECT     m.objid, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1,     n.objid, s.specObjID, bptclass,    o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2 into mydb.spectrabpt_final from MyDB.final_# AS m     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     JOIN PhotoObjAll AS o ON n.objid=o.objid    JOIN galSpecExtra AS s ON s.specObjID = o.specObjID
